2004-12-22  Martin Bravenboer <martin@cs.uu.nl>

	* configure.ac: The SDF tools of the ASF+SDF Meta-Environment
	1.5.3 require a new package tide-support. Hence, this package is
	now also part of the sdf2-bundle.

	* configure.ac: using the XT_ARG_WITH macro for the configuration
	of the ATerm library. Using XT_PKG_ATERM to check for the
	existance of the ATerm library at the specified prefix.

	* configure.ac: using XT_PRE_RELEASE.

	* NEWS: I should maintain NEWS.
	
	* ChangeLog: I should maintain the ChangeLog.

	* bootstrap: use autoreconf

	* get-subpackages.sh: no longer used.

